</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-jHkVzv iFnjrD pf-24_ pf-text-1"><strong>Advocacy</strong> - The RCN is crucial in lobbying for improved working conditions, fair pay, and better funding for nursing education.

</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-jHkVzv iFnjrD pf-26_ pf-text-1"><strong>Education and training</strong> - The RCN offers an extensive range of continuing professional development (CPD) opportunities to ensure nurses are equipped with the latest knowledge and skills.

