</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dVNjXY jGYlKM pf-34_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-jHkVzv iFnjrD pf-35_ pf-text-1"><strong>Royal College of Nursing (RCN)</strong> - A professional body and trade union representing nurses and nursing staff in the UK.


</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-jHkVzv iFnjrD pf-37_ pf-text-1"><strong>Continuing Professional Development (CPD)</strong> - Ongoing education and training activities that enable healthcare professionals to maintain and enhance their skills.

</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-jHkVzv iFnjrD pf-39_ pf-text-1"><strong>Legislation and regulations</strong> - Legal requirements and standards governing the practice of nursing and healthcare delivery.







